member.name: F:ESRI.ArcGIS.NetworkAnalyst.esriNALocationAllocationProblemType.esriNALAPTMinimizeWeightedImpedance
member.summary: Chooses N facilities that will minimize the sum of weighted costs between the facilities and demand points (PMedian).

member.name: F:ESRI.ArcGIS.NetworkAnalyst.esriNALocationAllocationProblemType.esriNALAPTMaximizeCoverage
member.summary: Chooses N facilities that will reach all demand points within a specified cutoff. Once all demand points have been reached the sum of weighted costs between the facilities and demand points will be minimized.

member.name: F:ESRI.ArcGIS.NetworkAnalyst.esriNALocationAllocationProblemType.esriNALAPTMaximizeCoverageMinimizeFacilities
member.summary: Chooses the minimum number of facilities necessary to reach all demand points. Solution facilities will minimize the sum of weighted costs between the facilities and demand points.

member.name: F:ESRI.ArcGIS.NetworkAnalyst.esriNALocationAllocationProblemType.esriNALAPTMaximizeAttendance
member.summary: Chooses N facilities that will maximize the demand point weight allocated to the facilities assuming that the allocated demand weight decreases with increased network distance.

member.name: F:ESRI.ArcGIS.NetworkAnalyst.esriNALocationAllocationProblemType.esriNALAPTMaximizeMarketShare
member.summary: Chooses N facilities that will maximize the market share of weighted demand points assuming the presence of competitor facilities. Uses a Huff model.

member.name: F:ESRI.ArcGIS.NetworkAnalyst.esriNALocationAllocationProblemType.esriNALAPTTargetMarketShare
member.summary: Chooses the minimum number of facilities necessary to achieve the target marketshare of weighted demand points assuming the presence of competitor facilities. Uses a Huff model.

member.name: F:ESRI.ArcGIS.NetworkAnalyst.esriNALocationAllocationProblemType.esriNALAPTMaximizeCapacitatedCoverage
member.summary: Chooses N facilities that will reach all demand points within a specified cutoff and subject to a per facility capacity constraint. The sum of weighted costs between the facilities and demand points will also be minimized.
